data.description: *Practically New* model-like home with updates galore! A gorgeous wrought iron door opens to an elongated foyer with entrance to a private study-2nd living-5th bedroom. Open concept living with high ceilings, 9ft doors & stone fireplace that opens to the kitchen. A chef's dream kitchen with gas cooktop, upgraded vent hood, large island, 2 pantries and eat-in area. Designated dining is great for family dinners. Owner's retreat features large walk-in shower with seat, separate vanities and Texas-sized closet. Head upstairs to your game room and separate media room that is pre-wired for speakers. Covered patio & low maintenance backyard. Welcome Home!
